<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head><meta charset="UTF-8"><title>Page expirée — EnMémoire.com</title></head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#F4F6F9;font-family:'Segoe UI',Arial,sans-serif;">
<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="padding:32px 16px;">
<tr><td align="center">
<table width="560" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"
       style="background:white;border-radius:16px;box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(27,43,75,.1);overflow:hidden;max-width:560px;width:100%;">

  <tr><td style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#7F1D1D,#991B1B);padding:28px 32px;text-align:center;">
    <h1 style="color:white;font-weight:300;font-size:22px;margin:0;">
      ❌ <span style="color:#FCA5A5;">En</span>Mémoire<span style="color:#FCA5A5;">.com</span>
    </h1>
  </td></tr>

  <tr><td style="padding:32px;">
    <h2 style="color:#1B2B4B;font-size:20px;font-weight:400;margin:0 0 12px;">
      Votre page mémorielle a expiré
    </h2>
    <p style="color:#6B7280;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;margin:0 0 20px;">
      Bonjour <strong style="color:#1B2B4B;">{{ owner.firstName }}</strong>,
      la page mémorielle de <strong style="color:#1B2B4B;">{{ page.deceasedFullName }}</strong>
      n'est plus accessible au public suite à l'expiration de votre abonnement.
    </p>
    <div style="background:#FEE2E2;border-left:4px solid #EF4444;border-radius:8px;padding:12px 16px;margin-bottom:24px;">
      <p style="margin:0;font-size:.875rem;color:#991B1B;">
        ❌ Vos données sont conservées. Renouvelez pour réactiver immédiatement la page.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div style="text-align:center;">
      <a href="{{ renewal_url }}"
         style="display:inline-block;background:#1B2B4B;color:white;text-decoration:none;
                padding:14px 32px;border-radius:8px;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;">
        🔄 Réactiver la page
      </a>
    </div>
  </td></tr>

  <tr><td style="background:#F8F4EE;border-top:1px solid #E8E0D4;padding:14px 32px;text-align:center;">
    <p style="color:#9CA3AF;font-size:12px;margin:0;">© {{ "now"|date("Y") }} EnMémoire.com</p>
  </td></tr>

</table>
</td></tr>
</table>
</body>
</html>
